# display: a header on its own never activates the display.  Spec: display.md
# "It is not possible to just display a header." With no `text` and no `value`
# there is no body content, so the circuit makes no write attempt and D1 stays OFF.
tickrate 100
patch <<<
[db8e]
[display]
    header = "ONLY"
>>>
@0 expectdisplay D1 off
@3 expectdisplay D1 off
